data.description: Stunning 2-Flat Greystone  For Sale in the HOT-HOT North Lawndale neighborhood!!! both floors are recently rehabbed and move-in ready! This is a GREAT investment for the owner occupant or savvy investor with multiple paying rents in the building. Investment Opportunity? Live in one of the units and rent the other. Get Top rents for these units for sure!! The first and Second-floor have 3BD/1BA.  All units have spacious open floor plans with living & dining rooms, kitchen, and hardwood floors throughout. Turn-key ready for your new tenant/tenants!! All separate utilities, gas forced-air furnaces. Recent improvements include. The property & location can't be beat! Walk to the parks, schools, shopping, public transportation and much more...
